{"tid":549502,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【中華小姐】阿田撐本地薑搞錯名 雷莊𠒇變莊端兒","createTime":"2018-02-03T16:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T06:11:41.000Z","uid":137470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3414d684e88ab1c12a10ad3483926d9951ac74","tid":549502,"uid":137470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T16:25:17.000Z","msg":"《2018年中華小姐競選》已經開始，由於今屆佳姐廣東話水平極差，被外間笑今屆為譚仔小姐選舉，由於雷莊𠒇是眾多佳麗當中廣東話較好，所以有不少網民都睇好雷莊𠒇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20180203/large/1517663188_a01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20180203%2Flarge%2F1517663188_a01b.jpg&h=ad23f97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比賽開場不久，一眾華麗評判團同在場觀眾都寧願選紐約劉思佳以及溫哥華伍殷嬅，而本地薑雷莊𠒇就僅得評判田蕊妮開咪撐。不過估唔到<span style=\"color: red;\">田蕊妮竟然將雷莊𠒇個名讀錯成莊端兒</span>，隨即被網民瘋狂恥笑。雖然阿田都即時望一望返個名，亦都心知自己講錯，但佢依然當冇事發生，繼續回答袁文傑問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180203/570681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180203%2F570681&d=pxqjvrwE%2Fn6xDQDs0E9K2EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=156fc5c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180203%2F570681&h=f83deab7\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180203/570681</a>"},{"pid":"8d87b941e5827f2553d548f2682ea1e781f9f050","tid":549502,"uid":33325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T16:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/005148_c0593fad7f3195913e16ff7eb2593816.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F005148_c0593fad7f3195913e16ff7eb2593816.png&h=2d0449ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37d71aa61322d5214a9970246c889a12f10dc1cb","tid":549502,"uid":56758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"莊端兒仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250c684c6a3958962261484470c176c82743f1a5","tid":549502,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:09:48.000Z","msg":"咁莊端兒真係正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20160317/large/1458217886_409f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160317%2Flarge%2F1458217886_409f.jpg&h=23fac1f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f2510782c454e9c3aa8c4bfd16a373b0e07c9d6","tid":549502,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:11:41.000Z","msg":"莊瑞兜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}